troduced in every village.<ref>{{cite web |title=5 Coin Master Tips & Tricks You Need to Know |url=https://heavy.com/games/2019/03/coin-master-game-tips-guide/ |website=heavy.com |publisher=Heavy}}</ref>\n\nThe game also features other mythological characters such as wizards, witches, warriors, and queens.<ref name=gazettereview/>\n\n===Pets===\nFoxy, Tiger, and Rhino are the 3 pets that are designed to help players collect more coins each in their own unique way. Pets can be raised by obtaining treats for them and raising their XP ([[experience point]]s) by using XP potions. Pets can also have eggs that can be hatched. Additionally, pets need to be kept awake with treats. They can stay awake for longer periods of time with multiple treats.<ref name=gameplay/>\n\n==Commercial==\nAs of October 2019, Coin Master has grossed over $508 million in gross revenue. 85% of Coin Master's net revenue comes from the U.S, the UK and Germany combined - over $260 million from the United States, a dramatic jump in the UK (since February 2019) resulting in $80 million, and Germany close behind with $52 million. Coin Master surpassed [[Candy Crush Saga]] as top-grossing game and claimed first place on both the App Store and Google Play store in the United Kingdom and Ireland.<ref>{{cite news |title=These are the iPhone's most popular apps |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/iphone-best-apps-2019-apple-app-store-most-popular-a9230706.html |work=The Independent |date=3 December 2019 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Forde |first1=Matthew |title=Weekly global mobile games charts: Coin Master overtakes Candy Crush Saga in Great Britain and Ireland for top grossing |url=https://www.pocketgamer.biz/asia/news/70042/weekly-global-mobile-games-charts-coin-master-overtakes-candy-crush-saga-in-great-britain-and-ireland-for-top-grossing/ |work=[[Pocket Gamer]]}}</ref>\n\nAccording to the website [[OMR Festival|OMR]], Moon Active earned $US 280 million un