irus: Iran has no plans to quarantine cities, Rouhani says |date=26 February 2020 |work=[[BBC News]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"BBqei\">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/06/chinese-schools-reopen-as-coronavirus-cases-in-europe-continue-to-rise |title=Iran threatens use of force to restrict spread of coronavirus |first1=Sam |last1=Jones |first2=Patrick |last2=Wintour |date=6 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HhmZ1\">{{cite news |first1=Ramin |last1=Mostaghim |first2=Mostafa |last2=Salem |first3=Tamara |last3=Qiblawi |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/02/26/middleeast/iran-coronavirus-intl/index.html |title=Iran was already struggling with one crisis. Now it has the worst coronavirus outbreak in the Middle East |date=26 February 2020 |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HHOnl\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/24/world/middleeast/coronavirus-iran.html |title='Recipe for a Massive Viral Outbreak': Iran Emerges as a Worldwide Threat |date=24 February 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]] |first1=David D. |last1=Kirkpatrick |first2=Farnaz |last2=Fassihi |first3=Mujib |last3=Mashal}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"oXjW2\">{{cite news |first1=Sam |last1=Jones |first2=Aamna |last2=Mohdin |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/feb/24/coronavirus-dead-in-iranian-city-of-qom |title=Coronavirus: Iran denies cover-up as six deaths reported in Italy |work=[[The Guardian]] |date=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"D2Xpc\">{{cite news |title=Coronavirus pummels Iran leadership as data show spread is far worse than reported |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/coronavirus-pummels-iran-leadership-as-data-show-spread-is-far-worse-than-reported/2020/03/04/7b1196ae-5c9f-11ea-ac50-18701e14e06d_story.html |work=[[The Washington Post]] |date=4 March 2020 |first1=Erin |last1=Cunningham |first2=Dalton |last2=Bennett}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"fXv2K\">{{cite web |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/8-percent-iran-parliament-has-